high_descs: Go to the sidetable under the television.
Open the microwave door. Place the apple on the left side. Close the microwave. Turn on the microwave for 4 seconds. Open the microwave door. Take out the apple.
Go to the fridge with doors.
Open the doors. Place the apple on the second level, on the left at the bottom of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Find an apple and take it to the fridge with doors.

high_descs: Turn right go straight walk to the side table
Take the apple from the side table
Turn left go straight turn right to the microwave
Put the apple in the microwave heat it and take it back
Turn left go straight turn right to the fridge
Put the apple in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Take the apple from the side table heat it and Put the apple in the fridge

high_descs: Turn back and walk, then turn left and walk towards the tv stand.
Pick up the apple from the tv stand.
Turn left and walk towards the microwave.
Put the apple into the microwave, heat it up, then pick it up back.
Turn right and walk, then turn left towards the fridge.
Put the apple, on the back side of the lettuce, in the top rack of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple into the fridge.
